---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About LeadFair — Built by a Small Business Owner"
  description="LeadFair is AI-powered business management software built by a small business owner who needed it first. Founded by Jeremy Turner in Huntsville, Alabama."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-blue py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="blob blob-blue w-72 h-72 -top-20 -right-20"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-green w-56 h-56 bottom-0 left-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="gradient-text-blue-green">I Built the Product</span><br/>
        <span class="gradient-text-blue-green">I Needed as an Owner</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">LeadFair started as a set of tools I built for my own business. Now it's a product so every small business owner can have the same thing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8">
            <span class="gradient-text-blue-green">The Story</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I'm Jeremy Turner. I own a music school in Huntsville, Alabama called Alabama Music Academy. After years of running it, I hit a wall that a lot of small business owners know well: I was spending more time on admin, phone calls, and marketing than on the actual work I started the business to do.
            </p>
            <p>
              Missed calls were costing me students. Manual scheduling was eating my evenings. And when it came to being found online? I was barely visible, even though I'd been in business for years.
            </p>
            <p>
              So I started building solutions. An AI phone agent to handle calls. Automations to eliminate busywork. A visibility strategy that actually worked for a local business. And it clicked — these weren't just solving my problems. They could solve the same problems for thousands of small businesses.
            </p>
            <p>
              That's LeadFair. I took everything that worked for my business — the AI receptionist, the automations, the visibility systems — and packaged it into a product that any small business owner can sign up for and start using. No consultants, no six-month timelines. Just a platform that learns your business and runs things for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <!-- Visual placeholder for Jeremy's photo -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-blue-green rounded-3xl p-1">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-400 to-secondary-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <span class="text-white text-4xl font-extrabold">JT</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Jeremy Turner</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light text-sm mb-4">Founder, LeadFair</p>
              <p class="text-text-lighter text-sm">Small business owner. Music educator. Product builder.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-gradient-blue-green">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dots opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">What We Believe</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-blue w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Results-Driven</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We measure success by what changes for your business, not by how impressive the technology sounds. If it doesn't move the needle, it's not in the product.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-green">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Human-First</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">AI should make things better for your customers, not creepier. LeadFair builds systems that feel helpful and natural, because that's what actually works.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-orange">
          <div class="icon-box icon-box-orange w-14 h-14 rounded-xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Practical Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We're not chasing the latest AI trend. LeadFair uses proven tools in smart ways, tailored to real business problems. Practical beats flashy every time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-dark opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-blue w-64 h-64 -top-20 -left-20 opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-green w-48 h-48 bottom-0 right-10 opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        See what LeadFair can do for your business. Pick a plan, or try one of our free tools first.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/pricing"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all text-lg btn-scale shadow-glow-orange"
        >
          See Pricing
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all text-lg btn-scale"
        >
          Get in Touch
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
